<div class="title">Clear Mind, With Strong Hallucinations</div>
<div class="substance">2C-T-2</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=Melinda&Exact=1">Melinda</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; Melinda. "Clear Mind, With Strong Hallucinations: An Experience with 2C-T-2 (exp18252)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Oct 17, 2002. erowid.org/exp/18252</div>

<br/>



<div class="report-text-surround">
